Trinity::

Growling, she tried to reach Burning Hammer to try to bite him. Her 
left leg wouldn't work, and she winced at the effort to walk.  "Your 
not a nice bot.  I don't want you to hurt my friends. Leave us alone 
you big bully."
She was a few feet away from BH, but wasn't going to give up.
